There are three '''"Paintings"''', the first unlocks at the start of the event, the others are unlocked day by day. You can get the following rewards after completing the paintings:
*Painting No.1: 3x Random T3 Skillbooks [[File:UnknownT3Book.png|30px]]
*Painting No.2: 4x Random T3 Plates [[File:UnknownT3Plate.png|30px]]
*Painting No.3: [[Akashi]]'s ''"Welcome to AzurCon!"'' [[File:AkashiEventIcon.png|30px]]

